*kbiff-3.8 (19 Mar 2006)

  19 Mar 2006; <ticho@gentoo.org> +kbiff-3.8.ebuild:
  Version bump. Closes bug #106227, reported by Jiri Tyr <jiri.tyr at
  e-learning.vslib.cz>.

  01 Aug 2005; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.1.ebuild:
  Depend on kdelibs instead of kdebase-meta. Bug #83058.

  05 Jun 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

  31 May 2005; Marcus D. Hanwell <marcus@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64.

  28 May 2005; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable on SPARC.

  15 Jan 2005; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.6.3.ebuild,
  kbiff-3.7.1.ebuild, kbiff-3.7.ebuild:
  Changed dep on kdebase to accept kdebase-meta, the split 'meta' package.
  This dep will be narrowed down in the future to the precise split packages
  required.

  16 Dec 2004; Simone Gotti <motaboy@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.1.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

  06 Dec 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.1.ebuild,
